		<img src="icon_posticon.gif" border="0" hspace="3"><font color="midnightblue" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="1">Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;04/16/2002&nbsp;:&nbsp; 09:22:26</font>

